overview.en: BMN Chain is a fair, convenient, efficient and safe new commercial ecological public chain based on the underlying technology of block chain. As an ecosystem of disparate applications, it will build a chain alliance that will provide basic services for parallel chains of unlimited scale, ecology and performance.
overview.zh: BMN Chain是基于区块链底层技术，为服务商业领域打造的公平、便捷、高效、安全的全新商业生态公链。作为一个由一系列分散应用程序组成的生态系统，它将打造一个公链联盟，为各条平行公链提供基础服务，无限拓展规模、生态和性能。
